{"tid":251223,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"見到呀妹比個MK中出左 點算好","createTime":"2017-05-20T17:16:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-21T01:52:51.000Z","uid":36906,"like":9,"dislike":162,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"73bf15573768170188227fa93e023bdd4680c1ec","tid":251223,"uid":36906,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T17:16:50.000Z","msg":"是咁的 岩岩同班fd落lkf 傾左一陣 個番左大陸既老母打黎<br />\n<br />\n老母:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :喂允兒呀 我岩岩出門口唔記得熄火 呀你快D番去熄火啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 下我過左海哦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  呀妹呢?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :佢去左camp wor<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁好啦<br />\n<br />\n一開門 見到 個MK一到屌我呀妹 一到望住我<br />\n我望住呀妹心諗 屌你老母 你唔係去左camp 咩 <br />\n難得我放假去泡 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :個MK<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 妹<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :唔係咁開心呀?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 唔係... 唔開心...<br />\n<br />\n跟住個MK開始著番褲<br />\n個妹仲好驚咁望住我<br />\n佢個閪仲有D精係到<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 我呀哥有6  packs嫁你快D走<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 下唔撚係掛咁好打?<br />\n之後佢一個轉身就唔知去閃左邊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :果個MK邊個黎?<br />\n<br />\n佢無應我<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跟手我就沖左入廚房 果然真係未熄火 <br />\n個爐頭仲燒熔左<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我想大家有無好既師傅介紹比我整番好佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95992127dc0e8b8cba7cd84bfe6f79a8874caa2d","tid":251223,"uid":1582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T17:18:09.000Z","msg":"整返個moon"},{"pid":"e719b5446151c36f2480cc5cc73b7eabd67cfe3a","tid":251223,"uid":17081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T17:19:06.000Z","msg":"搵胡師傅"},{"pid":"025e422c2052751f5fc4037f6fa9884bec09af27","tid":251223,"uid":52276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T17:19:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>是咁的 岩岩同班fd落lkf 傾左一陣 個番左大陸既老母打黎<br />\n<br />\n老母:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :喂允兒呀 我岩岩出門口唔記得熄火 呀你快D番去熄火啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 下我過左海哦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  呀妹呢?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :佢去左camp wor<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁好啦<br />\n<br />\n一開門 見到 個MK一到屌我呀妹 一到望住我<br />\n我望住呀妹心諗 屌你老母 你唔係去左camp 咩 <br />\n難得我放假去泡 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :個MK<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/